CREATE proc [dbo].[Usp_InsertStudentInfo] --Usp_InsertStudentInfo 0,'hh','jj','M',getdate(),getdate(),getdate(),'kk','hh','jj','M','add',2,0,1,0
@ID int,
@Name Varchar(100),
@Password Varchar(50),
@Gender Varchar(10),
@CreatedOn datetime=null,
@DateofJoining datetime=null,
@Birthdate datetime=null,
@EmailID Varchar(50)=null,
@FatherName Varchar(100)=null,
@MotherName Varchar(100)=null,
@Mobileno Varchar(12)=null,
@Address Varchar(100)=null,
@RoleID int=2,
@IsDleted bit=0,
@StudentClassID int = 1
as
begin
declare @joiningSession int=(select Value from DropDown where Category='Session' and @DateofJoining between StartDate and EndDate),
@maxRegistrationNo int=(Select max(RegistrationNo) from tbl_user),
@RegistrationNo int, @username varchar(100), @currentSession int,@RegistrationID int
if(isnull(@ID,0)=0)
begin
	if(@maxRegistrationNo is null or @maxRegistrationNo<0)
	begin
		set @RegistrationNo=1001
		end
	else 
	begin
		set @RegistrationNo=@maxRegistrationNo+1
		end
	set @currentSession =(select Value from DropDown where Category='Session' and GETDATE() between StartDate and EndDate)
	insert into tbl_user(Name,Mobileno,EmailID,Password,Gender,Birthdate,DateofJoining,Address,MotherName,FatherName
	,RoleID,StudentClassID,CreatedOn,IsDleted,JoiningSessionID,RegistrationNo)
	values (@Name,@Mobileno,@EmailID,@Password,@Gender,@Birthdate,@DateofJoining,@Address,@MotherName,@FatherName,@RoleID,
	@StudentClassID,@CreatedOn,@IsDleted,@joiningSession,@RegistrationNo)
	SET @RegistrationID = SCOPE_IDENTITY()
	set @username=(select case when (CHARINDEX(' ', Name))=0 then Name else SUBSTRING(Name, 1, CHARINDEX(' ', Name) - 1) end from tbl_user where RegistrationID=@RegistrationID)
	update tbl_user set username=CONCAT(@username, @RegistrationID) where RegistrationID=@RegistrationID
	if(@joiningSession=@currentSession)
	begin
	--updatedBy field pending
		insert into Tbl_StudentSessionDetails(RegistrationID,Name,SessionID,ClassID,IsBackDateUpdation,CreatedDate,IsDeleted,PromotionStatus)
		values(@RegistrationID,@Name,@joiningSession,@StudentClassID,0,GETDATE(),0,2)
	end
	
end
else
begin
	update tbl_user set
	Name=@Name,Mobileno=@Mobileno,EmailID=@EmailID,Password=@Password,Gender=@Gender,Birthdate=@Birthdate,Address=@Address,
	MotherName=@MotherName,FatherName=@FatherName,RoleID=@RoleID,StudentClassID=@StudentClassID,IsDleted=@IsDleted
	where RegistrationID=@ID
	if(@RoleID<>2)
	 update tbl_user set
		DateofJoining=@DateofJoining,JoiningSessionID=@joiningSession
		where RegistrationID=@ID
end
select @RegistrationID
end
